commmon
    - contains basic defines and typedefs used across the project 

core_base
    - contains a modular base class for CPU core functionalities

core_policies
    - contains core specific policies implementations using templates to emulate CPU instructions

core
    - contains the main CPU core implementation

memory
    - contains memory management and emulation components
    - 2KB SRAM (WRAM) + 62KB memory mapped components (PPU, APU, ...) = 64KB address space (16-bit addr field)
    - only 49120 bytes of the cartridge data can be accessed, for e.g., "Super Mario Bros" 32KB Program ROM, 8KB Character ROM = 40KB, + 3KB WRAM

register
    - contains CPU register definitions and utilities

ppu
    - 